  "title": "Customer Service Executive (Entry Level welcome, Freight forwarding, Mass Hiring!) [Bukit Merah | 5 days | up to $3500] - LCYL",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Customer Service Officer (Freight forwarding)</strong></h3><p><strong>5 days, 8.30am - 5.30pm/ 8.30am-5pm (Friday)</strong></p><p><strong>Salary: $2500 - $2800 (Entry Level)</strong><br /><strong>            $3000 - $3500 </strong></p><p><strong>Location: Bukit Merah Central, Singapore 159835</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Job scope:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Handle full sets of shipping documents (PSA/Customs/Tradenet/Portnet)</li><li>Handle day to day operations and transaction in the forwarding area.</li><li>Arrange bookings for shipping documents e.g.shipping orders, shipping notes, B/L etc</li><li>Ensure timely dispatch of shipping documents.</li><li>Responsible for timely invoicing, insurance of credit notes, internal expenses report and month end closing.</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>With 1-2 years of relevant experience in freight forwarding</li><li>Diploma in logistics</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Cheong Yeat Long | R25145358</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</p>",
